     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="4"/>
   <head>¶To the Gentl<gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
         <desc>•</desc>
      </gap>men Readers.</head>
   <p>
      <seg rend="decorInit">H</seg>Etherto Gentlemen I haue writte of
loues▪ and I haue found you fauorable
at the least smiling at my labours, <gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 word">
         <desc>〈◊〉</desc>
      </gap>
a plausible silence; now least I might
be thought to tie my sel<gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="2 letters">
         <desc>••</desc>
      </gap> wholly to a<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>morous
c<gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
         <desc>•</desc>
      </gap>nceites, I haue aduen<gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
         <desc>•</desc>
      </gap>ured
to discouer my conscience in Religion. If I write bare<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ly
in this Theological Phrase, as in al others, so I craue
your fauourable patience, which if you grante, I haue
my desire, and promise recompenc<gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
         <desc>•</desc>
      </gap> in what I may, e<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>uer,
and euery way to rest</p>
   <closer>
      <signed>yours. Robert Gr<gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="4 letters">
            <desc>••••</desc>
         </gap>.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
